= iff(tostring(recommendations.HtmlUrl) == \"\" or tostring(recommendations.HtmlUrl) == \"N/A\", \"\",  tostring(recommendations.HtmlUrl))\r\n| extend Name = tostring(properties.displayName)\r\n| project RiskLevel, Source, Organization, Project, Repo, Name, Tool, branch, CreatedAt ",
